%D A057655 E. Kraetzel, Lattice Points, Kluwer, Dordrecht, 1988.
%D A057655 C. D. Olds, A. Lax and G. P. Davidoff, The Geometry of Numbers, Math. Assoc. Amer., 2000, p. 51.
